            </div>
            <div id="faq2" class="collapse faq-answer">
                Most residential installations are completed within a few days, depending on the building size and site conditions.
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2618/2618540.png" class="faq-icon" alt="FAQ Symbol">
                <button class="faq-question" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
