            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2618/2618540.png" class="faq-icon" alt="FAQ Symbol">
                <button class="faq-question" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq6">
                    What if it is a cloudy day, it won't work, right?
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="faq6" class="collapse faq-answer">
                Solar panels still produce energy on cloudy days, just at a lower efficiency. Modern systems are designed to capture even diffused sunlight.
            </div>
        </div>
